<div class="ClassDoc YAMLDoc" id="basejoystick" markdown="1">

# class __basejoystick__

If you insert the `joystick` plugin at the start of your experiment, a
`joystick` object automatically becomes part of the experiment object
and can be accessed from within an inline_script item as `exp.joystick`.

__Function list:__


- [function __basejoystick.\_\_init\_\___(experiment, device=0, joybuttonlist=None, timeout=None)](#function-__basejoystick__init____experiment-device0-joybuttonlistnone-timeoutnone)
