<div class="FunctionDoc YAMLDoc" id="basejoystick-__init__" markdown="1">

## [function __basejoystick.\_\_init\_\___(experiment, device=0, joybuttonlist=None, timeout=None)](#function-__basejoystick__init____experiment-device0-joybuttonlistnone-timeoutnone) {#function-__basejoystick__init____experiment-device0-joybuttonlistnone-timeoutnone}

Intializes the joystick object.

__Arguments:__

- `experiment` -- An Opensesame experiment.
	- Type: experiment

__Keywords:__

- `device` -- The joystick device number.
	- Default: 0
	- Type: int
- `joybuttonlist` -- A list of buttons that are accepted or `None` to accept all
buttons.
	- Default: None
	- Type: list, NoneType
- `timeout` -- An timeout value in milliseconds or `None` for no timeout.
	- Default: None
	- Type: int, float, NoneType

</div>

