<div class="FunctionDoc YAMLDoc" id="basejoystick-get_joybutton" markdown="1">

## [function __basejoystick.get_joybutton__(joybuttonlist=None, timeout=None)](#function-__basejoystickget_joybutton__joybuttonlistnone-timeoutnone) {#function-__basejoystickget_joybutton__joybuttonlistnone-timeoutnone}

Collects joystick button input.

__Keywords:__

- `joybuttonlist` -- A list of buttons that are accepted or `None` to default joybuttonlist.
	- Default: None
	- Type: list, NoneType
- `timeout` -- A timeout value in milliseconds or `None` to use default timeout.
	- Default: None
	- Type: int, float, NoneType

__Returns:__

A (joybutton, timestamp) tuple. The joybutton is `None` if a timeout occurs.

- Type: tuple

</div>

